# Demo Builder — Panhandle Garage Door Company

## Status: COMPLETE

**Live demo:** https://api.michaelwegter.com/demos/panhandle-garage-door-company/

Full production WordPress site for Dimitroff Door Repair — SEO-first architecture with real content, LocalBusiness schema, Yoast SEO, 12 city landing pages, 8 service sub-pages, and an embedded live SEO audit tool.

