## SEO Implementation

- **LocalBusiness schema** in header.php: name, phone, postal address (120 Amherst Ave, Dumas TX 79029), openingHours (M-F 8-6, S-S 10-5), areaServed (12 cities), slogan "One Company. Every Door."
- **Yoast SEO:** auto-generates WebPage/BreadcrumbList/WebSite schema per page; SEO titles set
- **Content siloing:** `/services/` and `/service-area/` as WP parent pages
- **Internal linking:** home -> services -> service pages; city pages -> service pages; blog -> SEO audit page
- **Conversion:** click-to-call (806) 316-5296 every page, estimate form, mobile sticky bar (fixed bottom)
- **Remove canonical redirect:** `remove_filter('template_redirect', 'redirect_canonical')` in functions.php prevents sub-path proxy loop

---

## SEO Audit Tool Integration

`/free-seo-audit/` uses `page-seo-audit.php` WP template:
- Button: "Launch Free SEO Analyzer" -> https://mwegter95.github.io/free-seo-analyzer-with-js-rendering/ (200 live)
- Embedded `<iframe>` of same URL (950px height)
- Instructional copy: "Sign up with any email address and password (minimum 8 characters)"
- Suggested test URL shown: the demo site itself

